Source.Name: librecad
Source.Summary: LibreCAD is a free Open Source CAD application for Windows, Apple and Linux
Source.Description: LibreCAD is a 2D CAD drawing tool based on the community edition of QCAD. LibreCAD uses the cross-platform framework Qt, which means it works with most operating systems.
